Class BST12Adapt<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • BST12Adapt<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinSearchTree12<E>

    public class BST12Adapt<E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BinSearchTree12<E>
    BST12Adapt is the adapted class that adapts the TreeSet Class from the java collections framework. It implements BinSearchTree12, which is defined as a subset of the methods defined in the Java Collections Framework class Treeset, with 2 additional methods: height() and numChildren().
